    legacy: "Isaiah's prophecies of the Messiah were so detailed they read like eyewitness accounts, earning him the title 'the evangelical prophet.'",
    didYouKnow: "Isaiah 53, written 700 years before the crucifixion, describes Jesus's suffering so precisely that a Dead Sea Scroll copy of it—predating Jesus—left scholars astonished at its accuracy.",
    reflectionQuestion: "After experiencing God's forgiveness, are you willing to say 'Here am I, send me'?"
